        <p>India లో surgical oncologist కావాలంటే: MBBS (5.5 years), MS General Surgery (3 years), M.Ch Surgical Oncology (3 years). Total 11+ years dedicated training. General surgeon cancer operate చేయగలడు. కానీ cancer-specific decisions కి dedicated training required.</p>
